Adjust Your Intelligent Forecast Data

Need to account for a future promotion or upcoming event that could increase workload? Any new data that wasnâ€™t reflected in your workload history can be added to the forecast through an adjustment. You can also use an adjustment to remove certain data from your forecast.

Workforce Engagement is available in Lightning Experience, Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited Editions.

To adjust intelligent forecasts: Workforce Engagement Analyst user permission required.

Open Intelligent Forecasts in the App Launcher.
Click to open a forecast from the list view.
Scroll down to the Data Detail view.
Check the box next to a date.
Click Adjust.
Select Apply Percentage, Replace Data, or Skip Data.
Enter corresponding values if choosing to apply percentage or replace data.
Optionally, enter an adjustment reason.
Save your changes.
Click the Refresh dashboard icon to update your forecast.
title: Adjusting Intelligent Forecasts for Service Cloud
